      <scopecontent>
         <head>Collection Overview</head>
         <p>The University Finances Reference Collection contains files of publications, reports, news clippings, and memoranda related to the University's investments, fundraising, budgeting and other financial matters.  Major subjects include fundraising campaigns, and endowment management. The collection includes several publications produced to explain the University's finances to students. </p><!-- OPTIONAL: Use Arrangement clip here for Collection Arrangement section -->
      </scopecontent>
